<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="about-header">
                <h1>About SnapTrip</h1>
                <p class="lead">Your gateway to unforgettable travel experiences. Discover, explore, and create memories that last a lifetime.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-content">
                <section class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>At SnapTrip, we believe that travel should be accessible, safe, and enriching for everyone. Our mission is to connect travelers with authentic experiences while fostering a community of responsible tourism that benefits both visitors and local communities.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section">
                    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
                    <div class="features-grid">
                        <div class="feature-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                            <h3>Comprehensive Listings</h3>
                            <p>Discover thousands of verified travel listings from accommodations to experiences, all carefully curated for quality and authenticity.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                            <h3>Safety & Trust</h3>
                            <p>Every listing is verified, and we provide tools to ensure safe transactions and secure bookings for peace of mind.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                            <h3>Community Driven</h3>
                            <p>Join a vibrant community of travelers sharing reviews, tips, and recommendations to enhance your journey.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                            <h3>Seamless Experience</h3>
                            <p>Book and manage your trips effortlessly with our user-friendly platform available on all devices.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                    <p>We envision a world where travel breaks down barriers, creates understanding, and preserves the beauty of our planet. Through sustainable tourism practices and cultural exchange, we aim to make the world a smaller, more connected place.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded in 2020, SnapTrip began as a simple idea: to create a platform where travelers could find genuine, local experiences without the hassle of traditional booking sites. What started as a passion project has grown into a trusted community of millions of users worldwide.</p>
                    <p>Today, we continue to innovate and expand our offerings, always putting our users' needs first while maintaining our commitment to ethical tourism and environmental responsibility.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
.about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
}

.about-header h1 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.about-header .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #7f8c8d;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.about-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.about-section h2 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
}

.feature-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.feature-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.feature-item i {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #3498db;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.feature-item h3 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.feature-item p {
    color: #7f8c8d;
    line-height: 1.6;
}
</style>
